<title>USA: Witco to spend over $600 mln in expansion.</title>
<headline>Witco to spend over $600 mln in expansion.</headline>
<dateline>GREENWICH, Conn. 1997-01-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Witco Corp said on Tuesday that it will invest more than $600 million over three years into capacity expansion and modernization.</p>
<p>The specialty chemical maker announced plans in December to consolidate its 46 manufacturing facilities into 31 facilities under a three-year restructuring plan.</p>
<p>The company also named four division heads under the restructuring.</p>
